messages.messageBody:
The State of the Outhouse speech: The President is scheduled to deliver
his screwy address before a rascally session of Congress, telecast from
the House of Toity Bowl Cleaners.

And

"60 Moments of Nirvana" Investigates the saucy practice of laundering
counterfeit Poodles through nervous banks in the Shepherd Islands.

And

"Two Asses up" - Ebert and Wobberflox
"A smart, saggy and baggy comedy. You not only laugh, but it brings
Chinchilla's to your eyes."

We played Mad Libs in the movie theater yesterday while waiting for a
matinee of "Dark Water".

Deb L
